Description: SportOase - IServ module for booking sports facilities
 This IServ module provides a comprehensive booking system for school
 sports facilities with the following features:
  - Weekly schedule view with 6 customizable time periods
  - Student capacity management (max 5 students per booking)
  - Email notifications for bookings
  - Admin dashboard for oversight
  - Automatic weekend blocking
  - 60-minute advance booking requirement
  - Modern, mobile-responsive design with Tailwind CSS
  - PostgreSQL database with Doctrine ORM
  - Optional Google Calendar integration
